'''= attempt by Terry Hancock to implement a more effective incubator for free-licensed hardware development.''' 

URL = http://narya.narya.net/ [http://bazaar.narya.net/] [http://lspace.narya.net/]


=Description=

"Narya presently consists of three larger projects: the original Narya Project Incubator and Forum incorporates the basic CMS + forum concept, Bazaar is the e-commerce system, and LSpace  is to be an archive and cataloging system. It seems very likely that a fourth major component will need to be a collaborative CAD system. Narya is based on a Zope/Python web-application platform which pretty much takes care of the CMS infrastructure. I’m still working with Zope 2, but it seems likely that moving to Zope 3[26] will be a big help."
(http://www.freesoftwaremagazine.com/articles/free_matter_economy?page=0%2C2)



